This README file contains information on the contents of the
meta-backport-scarthgap layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Dependencies
============

  URI: https://git.yoctoproject.org/poky/meta
  branch: scarthgap

Patches
=======

Please submit any patches against the meta-backport-scarthgap layer via the
repository pull requests (https://github.com/gportay/meta-downstream/pulls).

Bugs
====

Please report any bugs against the meta-backport-scarthgap layer via the
repository issues (https://github.com/gportay/meta-downstream/issues).

Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-backport-scarthgap layer to your build
 II. Building the firmware

I. Adding the meta-backport-scarthgap layer to your build
=========================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-backport-scarthgap'

II. Building the firmware
=========================

Run 'bitbake core-image-minimal'
